A BILL
for
1 AN ACT relating to water and sewer districts; increasing
2 the cost requirements for water, sewer and water and sewer
3 district purchases or projects that are required to be
4 submitted for bids; specifying applicability; and providing
5 for an effective date.
6
7 Be It Enacted by the Legislature of the State of Wyoming:
